{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":22573,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真诚发问，如果性别事天生不可改变的，那么性别歧视是不是也可以说是天生的","timestamp":1592890449,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22581,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真诚发问，如果说黑皮肤是天生的不可改变的，那歧视黑皮肤是不是也可以说是天生的","timestamp":1592890475,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22588,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"大环境还是能改变很多的","timestamp":1592890507,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22595,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"对一种事物怀有偏见很正常，但大可不必歧视。这两个不是一种概念。就像你不喜欢吃青菜，你就不吃，但是不能把吃青菜的菜园子给砸了。平权目前最好的结果是论迹不论心，真正内心上的认同还需要很久，或者悲观来说根本不可能实现","timestamp":1592890522,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22608,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果说LGBT是天生的，那么就得首先说明是不是一种基因缺陷","timestamp":1592890580,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22629,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 嗯嗯有理","timestamp":1592890654,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22647,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 论迹不论心赞同 明面上我很尊重lgbt 其实我非常厌恶他们，因为他们在社交平台上太吵了，我不会禁止他们说话，他们却很喜欢禁止别人说话\n","timestamp":1592890731,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22648,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果天生就是无罪，那炼铜呢？","timestamp":1592890741,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22807,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis:  为什么你会只看到社交平台上LGBT在吵，你有想过这个问题吗？","timestamp":1592891321,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":22828,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3774,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 人们根本不需要说话，只需要维持现状，就可以永远继续对他们歧视下去啊？他们不为自己说，难道等着别人为他们说？按这个逻辑，所有民权运动不正当，在旁观者看来必然是只会喊口号的好斗分子。","timestamp":1592891397,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3774,"reply":10,"tag":null,"text":"真诚发问，如果说LGBT是天生的不可改变的，那歧视LGBT是不是也可以说是天生的","timestamp":1592890381,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}